on the souls of the dead.

23:21.024 --> 23:24.492
Both in an eternal quest
for the Mother of Evil

23:24.528 --> 23:27.128
who will release us
from our bondage

23:27.164 --> 23:29.998
and allow one of us
to reconquer Heaven

23:30.000 --> 23:33.218
and topple God
from his bloody throne.

23:33.253 --> 23:37.555
And so will the Darkness
reign, on Earth, in Heaven...

23:39.609 --> 23:41.042
