Sir Malcolm is himself again.

30:27.216 --> 30:29.717
He is full of anger...

30:30.920 --> 30:32.753
and will strike back.

30:35.224 --> 30:36.824
And so he will come...

30:38.811 --> 30:41.395
- in all his manly rage.
- And then?

30:43.099 --> 30:45.182
- You shall see.
- Tell me now.

30:47.570 --> 30:49.103
Careful, child.

30:50.239 --> 30:52.023
You grow impertinent.

30:52.075 --> 30:53.357
You grow old.

30:54.277 --> 30:55.676
- [Madame Kali growling]
- [gasps]

30:56.529 --> 30:58.579
Never forget who commands.

30:59.549 --> 31:01.032
[Hecate screams]

31:01.117 --> 31:02.533
[Hecate panting]

31:10.093 --> 31:12.793
[Madame Kali] And so
my chivalrous knight...

31:12.829 --> 31:14.128
