36:34.016 --> 36:35.783
Forever unchanging.

36:37.954 --> 36:40.254
My sins made manifest
only here.

36:43.676 --> 36:46.293
At times, I've deceived myself
into thinking, uh...

36:47.797 --> 36:49.263
I'm other than this.

36:52.468 --> 36:53.884
Don't we all want to
paint ourselves

36:53.936 --> 36:55.803
into something...

36:55.805 --> 36:57.438
better than we are?

36:59.859 --> 37:01.225
