37:13.155 --> 37:15.205
Can you accept me as I am?

37:19.662 --> 37:21.128
Can you love me?

37:23.799 --> 37:24.832
Yes.

37:39.598 --> 37:40.814
[gulps]

37:47.523 --> 37:48.689
[gasps]

37:55.531 --> 37:56.830
[choking]

38:01.137 --> 38:03.003
