39:04.834 --> 39:06.300
[Lily] Mmm.

39:14.110 --> 39:16.193
- [floorboards creaking]
- [Lily gasps]

39:17.830 --> 39:19.947
Mr. Clare, you startled me.

39:25.254 --> 39:27.121
I don't... I don't think
it's entirely proper

39:27.123 --> 39:29.373
