to my bed right now.

44:52.614 --> 44:54.581
I'll bleed for you.

44:55.784 --> 44:57.284
I'll love you...

44:58.954 --> 45:00.504
for your sadness...

45:01.790 --> 45:04.124
and your poetry
and your passion

45:04.176 --> 45:05.425
and your rage

45:05.928 --> 45:10.046
and your infinite,
luxurious ugliness.

45:11.216 --> 45:13.216
I'll lick your sins away.

45:16.221 --> 45:17.637
[Mr. Clare panting]

45:21.376 --> 45:23.443
And when Victor comes home...

45:26.865 --> 45:30.150
we'll put our hands
around his throat together...

45:31.870 --> 45:33.570
and watch him die.

45:35.874 --> 45:38.124
And then this will be
our home.

45:40.045 --> 45:41.328
And then?

45:43.215 --> 45:45.165
What then, undead thing?

45:49.171 --> 45:52.589
We were created to rule,
my love.

45:54.176 --> 45:58.512
And the blood of mankind
will water our garden.

46:00.015 --> 46:02.232
Us and our kin...

46:03.151 --> 46:04.518
and our children,

46:04.570 --> 46:06.436
and our generations.

46:07.656 --> 46:09.439
We are the conquerors.

46:10.859 --> 46:13.410
We are the pure blood.

46:13.445 --> 46:17.197
We are steel and sinew both.

46:17.199 --> 46:19.699
We are the next 1000 years.

46:20.419 --> 46:22.168
We are the dead.

46:32.881 --> 46:34.014
[panting]

46:36.885 --> 46:38.184
No being...

46:40.355 --> 46:43.607
who ever was...
or ever will be,

46:43.642 --> 46:45.225
shall love you...

46:46.395 --> 46:47.694
like I do.

47:08.083 --> 47:09.249
[Madame Kali] <i>Memory.</i>

47:11.553 --> 47:14.170
It is such a potent force
in our lives.

47:15.223 --> 47:17.090
All of these <i>memento mori...</i>

47:18.477 --> 47:20.260
for one sobering message...

47:21.530 --> 47:23.730
"Remember that you will die."

47:25.734 --> 47:28.168
