to lure a lion, don't you?

47:40.315 --> 47:42.716
So all I require of you
is that you...

47:43.752 --> 47:45.118
[mimics sheep bleating]

47:47.556 --> 47:48.755
Why Miss Ives?

47:48.790 --> 47:50.090
Because the Master
desires her.

47:50.892 --> 47:52.125
