I've found a kind of elation.

48:33.168 --> 48:36.036
To feel
the old touch of passion.

48:36.071 --> 48:37.554
To yearn.

48:40.058 --> 48:41.474
To be truly human.

48:41.510 --> 48:44.644
My humanity, such as it is,
is colder than this house.

48:44.680 --> 48:45.745
No.

48:47.149 --> 48:49.115
No arrogance or pride.

48:50.318 --> 48:53.319
This is your chance
to live, Malcolm.

48:54.523 --> 48:56.122
Let's bury the past together.

48:57.059 --> 49:00.060
Your wife... your son,

49:00.095 --> 49:02.862
your daughter,
and all my sins as well,

49:03.432 --> 49:05.165
which surely match your own.

49:05.200 --> 49:06.416
Far exceed them.

49:06.501 --> 49:08.835
[sobbing]
I don't want to live alone.

49:08.870 --> 49:10.036
Nor do you.

49:10.038 --> 49:12.756
Take my hand and love me.

49:12.791 --> 49:14.841
We have no one else.

49:14.876 --> 49:17.210
And together
we will walk quietly.

49:19.965 --> 49:21.131
[sniffling]

49:22.050 --> 49:24.300
So quietly.

49:25.387 --> 49:26.686
You know, if I could,

49:27.222 --> 49:29.773
I would tear
that beautiful head

49:29.808 --> 49:34.527
from your shoulders
and laugh all the while.

49:38.233 --> 49:40.400
But if you will let
Miss Ives live,

49:43.622 --> 49:45.955
I will walk with you
to the end of time.

49:46.625 --> 49:48.291
She means so much?

49:49.494 --> 49:51.044
She means all.

49:54.883 --> 49:56.716
It's the one thing
I cannot do.

49:57.753 --> 49:59.969
The Master will have her.

50:00.005 --> 50:03.089
Then when I have played
this game out, my dear...

50:04.593 --> 50:06.843
the lamb will kill the lion.

50:10.732 --> 50:12.198
I suppose
I shouldn't be surprised

50:12.234 --> 50:14.834
at your tiresome obsession
with Miss Ives.

50:14.870 --> 50:16.970
You're so very close
after all.

50:18.974 --> 50:21.040
You knew her
when she was born, didn't you?

50:21.076 --> 50:22.842
- Yes.
- You saw her grow

50:22.878 --> 50:24.878
into the fine young woman
she is?

50:25.313 --> 50:26.346
Yes.

50:27.649 --> 50:31.417
Yeah. You watched her
rather carefully, I'd say.

50:31.453 --> 50:32.452
Did I?

50:36.591 --> 50:38.258
Of course you did.

50:41.563 --> 50:43.363
She was always your favorite.

50:48.770 --> 50:50.637
It's good we care
for our daughters.

51:00.899 --> 51:02.699
Mind her, she stings.

51:03.819 --> 51:05.902
I'll leave you two
to catch up.

51:05.954 --> 51:07.070
One other thing.

51:07.656 --> 51:10.824
Our theme for tonight, yes?

51:13.662 --> 51:16.079
I'll leave you
with a few memories.

51:18.166 --> 51:19.465
Mind them.

51:20.719 --> 51:22.252
They sting too.

51:30.712 --> 51:32.178
[door closes]

52:12.604 --> 52:14.220
[exhales sharply]

52:25.901 --> 52:27.283
[sniffles]

53:02.520 --> 53:03.736
[sighs]

53:21.923 --> 53:23.373
[sobbing]

53:23.425 --> 53:25.041
Oh, Peter.

53:25.961 --> 53:27.293
Peter.

53:40.976 --> 53:42.308
[continues sobbing]

53:58.226 --> 53:59.625
[gasping]

